<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Academo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/mock-up.css">
    <script src="js/jquery-minified.js"></script>
    <script src="bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/mock-up.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="modal fade" id="profilePopup">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-vlg">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span><span class="sr-only">Close</span></button>
                    <div class="align-center">
                        <div class="nav-arrows inline-block">
                            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
                            <h2 class="inline-block"></h2>
                            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <ul class="media-list center-block" id="profile">
                        <li class="media">
                            <div class="pull-left thumbnail align-center" href="#">
                                <ul class="nav nav-pills">
                                    <li><a href="#" class="active">About Me</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#">Reviews/Comments</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="#">Calendar</a></li>
                                </ul>
                                <hr />
                                <span id="tutorMessagePopupModal0" data-id="startupId0"
                                      data-name="Clockworks" class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope pull-right envelope-big"></span>
                                <img src="/images/eraser.png" alt="Clockworks' Photo"><br>
                                <a class="cursor-pointer">Select And Book A Session</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="media-body">
                                <ul class="list-group inline-block">
                                    <li>Name: Ramesh G</li>
                                    <li>Degree: Materials Science and Engg</li>
                                    <li>Uni: IIT</li><br>
                                    <li>
                                        <p>
                                            In 1991, Shaka Senghor shot and killed a man. He was, he says, "a drug dealer with a quick temper and a semi-automatic

                                            pistol." Jailed for second degree murder, that could very well have been the end of the story. But it wasn't. Instead, it was

                                            the beginning of a years-long journey to redemption, one with humbling and sobering lessons for us all.This talk was pre-
                                            sented at an official TED conference, and was featured by our editors on the home page.In 1991, Shaka Senghor shot and

                                            killed a man. He was, he says, "a drug dealer with a quick temper and a semi-automatic pistol." Jailed for second degree

                                            murder, that could very well have been the end of the story. But it wasn't. Instead, it was the beginning of a years-long
                                        </p>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div><!-- /.modal-content -->
        </div><!-- /.modal-dialog -->
    </div><!-- /.modal -->

    <div id="pageHeader" class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-4 logo">
                <a href="#"><img src="/images/logo.jpg"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-3 col-xs-offset-5">
                <div id="loginBox" class="login-box row align-center">
                    <% if user_signed_in? %>
                        <div id="paypalTopUp" class="col-xs-5 top-up">TOP-UP</div>
                        <div class="col-xs-2"> <%= current_user.email %> </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-6"> <%= link_to('Logout', destroy_user_session_path, :method => :delete) %> </div>
                    <% else %>
                        <div class="col-xs-6"> <%= link_to('Register', new_user_registration_path) %> </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-6"> <%= link_to('Login', new_user_session_path) %> </div>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div id="menuBarHolder">
        <div id="menuBar" class="row align-center">
            <div class="col-xs-3 menu-item"><h4>About ACADEMO</h4></div>
            <div class="col-xs-2 menu-item"><h4>Faces</h4></div>
            <div class="col-xs-3 menu-item"><h4>Our Achievements</h4></div>
            <div class="col-xs-2 menu-item"><h4>Contact Us</h4></div>
            <div class="col-xs-2 menu-item"><h4>Blog</h4></div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <ul class="nav nav-pills align-center container">
            <li><a class="active">Personalised Tutorials</a></li>
            <li><a>Smart Classroom</a></li>
            <li><a>Start-up Consultation</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="pageBody">
        <div class="info-box" id="aboutAcademo">
            <h3 class="header align-center">How does it work?</h3>
            <h4 class="center-block align-center">
                <ol type="1" class="inline-block align-left">
                    <li>Search for a Subject/Tutor</li>
                    <li>Get Started!</li>
                </ol>
            </h4>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="searchBox" class="container">
        <div class="form-group row search-box">
            <div class="col-xs-7 col-xs-offset-1">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Physics or John" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-2">
                <button type="button" class="form-control">Search</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%= link_to 'New tutor', new_tutor_path %>

    <div id="searchResults" class="container">
        <ul class="media-list">
            <% @tutors.each do |tutor| %>
                <li class="media" id= <%= tutor.id %> >
                    <span id="tutorMessagePopup0" data-id= <%= tutor.id %>  data-name= <%= tutor.name %>  class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope pull-right envelope-big"></span>
                    <br>
                    <a class="pull-left" href="#">
                        <img class="media-object" src="/images/eraser.png" alt="Ramesh's Photo">
                    </a>
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <ul class="list-group inline-block">
                            <li><a class="profile-trigger cursor-pointer">Name: <%= tutor.name %> </a></li>
                            <li>Degree: <%= tutor.degree %> </li>
                            <li>Uni: <%= tutor.place %> </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <a id="tutorStartTuition0" class="pull-right cursor-pointer">Start Tuition</a>
                    <br>
                </li>
            <% end %>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div id="pageFooter"></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
